Current progress - I have got most of the dependencies installed - many by pip, but some I had to revert to Windows msi installers. Pad with details here: &lt;a class="ext-link" href="http://ckan.okfnpad.org/windows"&gt;&lt;span class="icon"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;http://ckan.okfnpad.org/windows&lt;/a&gt;. So far done: 1 day.
